extensions.description: Trade perpetuals with low costs and low latency on Ethereum L2 with custom ZK circuits for verifiable matching and liquidations.  Public mainnet live.

Step into the darkness with EDG – the official Netflix-partnered meme coin inspired by Monster: The Ed Gein Story. Releasing on 3/10/25, EDG blends true crime horror with Solana speed, delivering a cinematic experience on-chain. A cult narrative meets cutting-edge memes — backed by a community ready to write the next chapter of terror.
